A '''Legate''' was an assistant legislator in the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic]] and [[Galactic Alliance Senate]]s. Legates weren't allowed to vote in the Senate, but they were allowed to voice their concerns in session. Like [[Junior Representative/Legends|Associate Planetary Representatives]] in the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]], they represented affiliate groups.

